Fullfill the assignment requirements included bonus.
Use make to create executable files.
first, "./server" or "bash server.sh" to create server.
Then in other window:
 ./client put host port localFilename remoteFilename
 ./client get host port remoteFilename localFilename
Or use bash script:
 bash client.sh put host port localFilename remoteFilename
 bash client.sh get host port remoteFilename localFilename
as assignment describe.
